column5: Hey guys. Dying to find a place to try out our new hut. Does anyone know how thick the ice is at Virginia Beach?
From anything I have heard lots of ice .Still a good 8 to 10 inches.But with the rain keep your eye's open .Be safe out there.

Hey  I spent the day there yesterday,  tons of good black ice.   Dave\s fish huts are all out there and quite a few personal huts  all fishing.  I would say its safe, but becareful none the less  Dave
Thank you guys so much!  Lovetofish
Anyone coming up to Virginia Beach on Saturday?
